Package: GWASpost
Type: Package
Title: GWAS Post-Processing Toolkit for Glioma Analyses
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Huang", family = "Lab", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "maintainer@example.org")
)
Description: Utilities to convert the original glioma GWAS post-analysis scripts
    into reusable R package functions. The package starts with a full
    colocalization pipeline that accepts GWAS summary statistics and a local
    eQTL summary statistics directory.
